Package: detectRUNS
Type: Package
Title: Detect Runs of Homozygosity (RoHom) and Runs of Heterozygosity (RoHet) in
    diploid genomes
Version: 0.8.2
Date: 2017-06-13
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Filippo Biscarini <filippo.biscarini@ibba.cnr.it> [aut, cre]",
    "Gabriele Marras <gabriele.marras@ptp.it> [aut]",
    "Paolo Cozzi <paolo.cozzi@ptp.it> [ctb]"
  ))
Description: Detection of Runs of Homozygosity (RoHom) and of
    Heterozygosity (RoHet) in diploid genomes using two methods (sliding windows
    and consecutive runs).
